{"tid":1177164,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我對唔住你阿蚊","createTime":"2019-05-29T15:39:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-29T16:11:18.000Z","uid":80921,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"097a5f4fd1c041f9ee1c2dc4b46b925f6236115e","tid":1177164,"uid":80921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T15:39:18.000Z","msg":"屌你老尾，諗住休息下針鳩我。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你都有今日啦，比我拍暈左，拆哂佢啲手手腳腳落黎。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n比佢得返對翼同埋支針。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呀，我放近隻手指埋去佢支針度，佢又真係拍翼想針埋黎啵。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n依家佢未死，我要佢求生不得求死不能！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5fxTTHF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5fxTTHF.png&h=79268677&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"21e36308c854e318094c69531b40a73b4418048f","tid":1177164,"uid":80921,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T15:41:17.000Z","msg":"手術夾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0kEZPgB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0kEZPgB.png&h=b2b0777a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"55683460c9fbc7b5e469d51fca6d8a70a54ef0a9","tid":1177164,"uid":247912,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T15:42:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d4cedfb2b11447f42c12e5f7a6d3a03d96ac9917","tid":1177164,"uid":253039,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T15:45:14.000Z","msg":"以為叫春post 差啲就㩒咗負皮"},{"pid":"d72a1aae0eb0227830529a44bcb47f2f3ae99168","tid":1177164,"uid":80921,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"55683460c9fbc7b5e469d51fca6d8a70a54ef0a9","tid":1177164,"uid":247912,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019